OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,FThe UK's independent public advocate
OL,7,Fneeds more powers and resources, an MP
OL,8,Fwho has been a prominent voice for
OL,9,Fvictims of the Hillsborough disaster
OL,10,Ffor decades has said.
OL,12,FLabour former minister Maria Eagle,
OL,13,Ffor Liverpool Garston, made her case
OL,14,Fas the Government introduced the so-
OL,15,Fcalled Hillsborough Law in Parliament
OL,16,F` the Public Office (Accountability)
OL,17,FBill ` which will force public
OL,18,Fofficials and contractors to tell the
OL,19,Ftruth in the aftermath of disasters.
