OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,FThe law is named after the
OL,7,FHillsborough disaster, in which 97
OL,8,Ffootball fans died as the result of a
OL,9,Fcrush at the FA Cup semi-final between
OL,10,FLiverpool and Nottingham Forest at a
OL,11,Ffootball ground in Sheffield in 1989.
OL,13,FMs Eagle has repeatedly introduced
OL,14,Flegislation since 2016 seeking to
OL,15,Festablish an independent public
OL,16,Fadvocate (IPA) to be a voice for those
OL,17,Fwho have been bereaved in public
OL,18,Fdisasters, as well as for survivors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
