OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,FShe aimed to recreate the work of the
OL,7,FHillsborough Independent Panel set up
OL,8,Fin 2009, which she argued "succeeded
OL,9,Fspectacularly" where the legal system
OL,10,Fhad failed, and "finally had the truth
OL,11,Festablished in the public
OL,12,Fconsciousness that the South Yorkshire
OL,13,FPolice had tried to cover up for all
OL,14,Fthose years".
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@NO]rD@QOUvD@LO]
