OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,FThe role was eventually created
OL,7,Fthrough the Victims and Prisoners Act
OL,8,F2024 and the Government appointed
OL,9,FCindy Butts to take up the position to
OL,10,Fadvise victims of major disasters and
OL,11,Fsupport them through investigations,
OL,12,Finquests and inquiries.
OL,14,FHowever, Ms Eagle said the IPA does
OL,15,Fnot have the powers or resources she
OL,16,Fhad envisaged in her Bill.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
