OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,FThe Labour MP told the Commons on
OL,7,FMonday: "The Hillsborough Independent
OL,8,FPanel was not a legal proceeding. It
OL,9,Fwas about the transparent release of
OL,10,Fdocuments, freedom of information and
OL,11,Fa narrative account arising out of the
OL,12,Fstudy of the documents. There weren't
OL,13,Flawyers involved.
OL,15,F"The Bill I kept introducing to this
OL,16,Fhouse was to enable a public advocate
OL,17,Fin the event of disasters to assist
OL,18,Ffamilies to get to the truth much
OL,19,Fsooner, by being able to replicate
OL,20,Fsuch a process, but at a much earlier
OL,21,Fstage in the aftermath of disasters.
OL,26,@oD@IOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
