OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,F"I believe this will promote the
OL,7,Ftelling of truth at a much earlier
OL,8,Fstage, because shining the light of
OL,9,Ftransparency on the activity of public
OL,10,Fofficials in the aftermath of a
OL,11,Fdisaster will torpedo cover-ups before
OL,12,Fthey can get very far and at a
OL,13,Fsignificantly lower cost to the public
OL,14,Fpurse and faster than our justice
OL,15,Fsystem has shown itself able to manage.
OL,17,F"The Hillsborough Independent Panel
OL,18,Fdid it in two years, and they did in
OL,19,Ftwo years what the justice system had
OL,20,Ffailed to do in 24 years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
