OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,F"I think this kind of proceeding has
OL,7,Fthe potential to enable families to
OL,8,Fsidestep the years of overlapping
OL,9,Flegal actions they get caught up in
OL,10,Fafter public disasters, and I think it
OL,11,Fwill be a useful addition to the
OL,12,Farmoury of families who want the truth
OL,13,Fquickly, accountability quickly and
OL,14,Flessons to be learned.
OL,16,F"I think that families bereaved by
OL,17,Fpublic disasters should have an option
OL,18,Fof asking for such a process at a much
OL,19,Fearlier stage in the aftermath, and it
OL,20,Fshould be up to them if they want it
OL,21,Fto be done.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
