OL,3,CHillsborough Law Independent Advocate
OL,4,C'needs more powers'
OL,6,F"I believe provisions on the
OL,7,Findependent public advocate would
OL,8,Fincrease the range of options for
OL,9,Fbereaved families in the aftermath of
OL,10,Fpublic disasters like Hillsborough,
OL,11,Fwould mean that families have a
OL,12,Fgreater choice about how to take
OL,13,Fforward their efforts, and it would be
OL,14,Fa good addition."
